* What I'm searching for

20:23.723 --> 20:24.891
* To tell it straight

20:24.991 --> 20:28.461
* I'm trying to build a wall

20:28.561 --> 20:31.598
* Walking by myself

20:31.698 --> 20:37.270
* Down avenues that reek
of time to kill *

