[car horn honks]

20:39.472 --> 20:40.873
* Stop trying to catch my eye

20:40.973 --> 20:43.410
* I see you good
you forced faker *

20:43.510 --> 20:44.577
* You make it easy

20:44.677 --> 20:47.680
* You're my enemy,
you fast talker *

