*

21:11.704 --> 21:13.540
* If I could stand up mean

21:13.573 --> 21:13.606
Hi, I'm Danny Castellano...

21:17.544 --> 21:19.579
and I'm in love
with your daughter.

21:19.679 --> 21:22.315
* What am I here for?

21:22.415 --> 21:27.554
* I left my home
to disappear is all *

21:27.654 --> 21:30.390
* I'm here for myself

21:30.490 --> 21:34.461
* Not to know you,
I don't need no one else *

